			</p>
			<input type="text" name="url" id="url" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="Paste News Article URL...">
			<button class="w-50 btn btn-primary mt-4 mb-3 align-self-center">Analyze</button>
			<small class="w-100 text-center">Thanks!</small>
		</form>
	</div>

	<!-- How it Works? Container -->
	<article>
		<h2 class="h2">How it Works?</h2>
		<ol>
			<li>We parse the website, extracting the article</li>
			<li>We process key words and phrases using <a href="http://www.compromise.cool">compromise.cool</a></li>
			<li>Using that information, we rank each sentence as positive, neutral, or negative</li>
		</ol>
	</article>
